trans-unit.source: Provides a reusable <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.UserControl" /> object for editing <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.UserControl" /> reutilizável para editar objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> objects that are referenced by several different properties of controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> classe fornece uma interface do usuário para edição de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elementos de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> objetos que são referenciados por várias propriedades diferentes de controles em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> class encapsulates most of the functionality of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> classe encapsula a maioria das funcionalidades de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> consists of an enclosing form that holds the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>, and **OK** and **Cancel** buttons.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterCollectionEditor> consiste em um formulário de delimitador que contém o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>, e **Okey** e **Cancelar** botões.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> method adds an array of existing parameters to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> método adiciona uma matriz de parâmetros existentes para o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> method removes all parameters from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> método Remove todos os parâmetros do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> method gets all parameters from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> método obtém todos os parâmetros do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> method controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the parameters in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> método controla se as adições e exclusões podem ser feitas para os parâmetros de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> interface to the current design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Uma interface de <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> para o host de design atual, como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl" /> class using the specified <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl" /> usando o <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the component controls of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object, initializes UI elements, connects events for the individual component editors, and adds the component editors to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> collection for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.%23ctor%2A> construtor inicializa os controles de componente do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> objeto, inicializa os elementos de interface do usuário, se conecta a eventos para os editores de componente individual e adiciona os editores de componente para o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> coleta para o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter" /> array of existing parameters to add to the editor.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter" /> de parâmetros existentes a adicionar ao editor.

trans-unit.source: Adds an array of existing parameters to the editor.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona uma matriz de parâmetros existentes para o editor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> method adds the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements of `parameters` to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> método adiciona o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elementos de `parameters` para o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> controlar o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> objeto.

trans-unit.source: If there is more than one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> element, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> selects the first one in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>.
trans-unit.target: Se houver mais de um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elemento, o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> seleciona o primeiro no <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView>.

trans-unit.source: Then the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> refreshes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control and raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Em seguida, o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.AddParameters%2A> atualiza o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> controle e gera o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> evento.

trans-unit.source: Removes all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Remove todos os parâmetros do editor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> method removes the parameters from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> método Remove os parâmetros a partir o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> controlar o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Then the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> refreshes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control and raises the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Em seguida, o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ClearParameters%2A> atualiza o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> controle e gera o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection.ParametersChanged> evento.

trans-unit.source: Gets all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Obtém todos os parâmetros do editor.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter" /> array of all parameters from the editor.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter" /> de todos os parâmetros do editor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> method populates a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> array with all parameters from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.GetParameters%2A> método preenche uma <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> matriz com todos os parâmetros do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListView> controlar o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl>.

trans-unit.source: The source of the event.
trans-unit.target: A fonte do evento.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.EventArgs" /> object that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.EventArgs" /> que contém os dados do evento.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ParametersChanged" /> event when the state of a parameter in the editor changes.
trans-unit.target: Gera o evento <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.ParametersChanged" /> quando o estado de um parâmetro no editor muda.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when any parameter or one of the parameter's properties is changed.
trans-unit.target: Ocorre quando qualquer parâmetro ou uma das propriedades do parâmetro muda.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether all the parameters in the editor are configured.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se todos os parâmetros no editor estão configurados.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if all parameters in the editor are fully configured; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se todos os parâmetros no editor sejam configurados; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether additions and deletions can be made to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection" /> being edited.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> que indica se adições e exclusões podem ser feitas ao <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection" /> que está sendo editado.

trans-unit.source: Controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the values in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Controla se as adições e exclusões podem ser feitas para os valores no editor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> method controls whether additions and deletions can be made to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> método controla se as adições e exclusões podem ser feitas para o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ParameterCollection> elemento o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl> objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> enables or disables the Up, Down, Add, and Delete buttons but it does not affect the editing of individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elements.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl.SetAllowCollectionChanges%2A> habilita ou desabilita a para cima, para baixo, para adicionar e excluir botões, mas ele não afeta a edição de um indivíduo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter> elementos.

trans-unit.source: Provides metadata for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Fornece metadados para a classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ParameterEditorUserControl" />.

trans-unit.source: A type descriptor provider object.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto de provedor de descritor de tipo.
